{"word":"Jezreel","slug":"jezreel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jezreel</b> <a href=\"#/H3157\">H3157</a> <br/> 1. A city in southern Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=56'>Jos 15:56</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=25&verse=43'>1Sa 25:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=27&verse=3'>1Sa 27:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=29&verse=1'>1Sa 29:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=29&verse=11'>1Sa 29:11</a><br/> 2. A city of Issachar<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=18'>Jos 19:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=2&verse=9'>2Sa 2:9</a> <br/> - Ahab's residence in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=46'>1Ki 18:46</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=1'>1Ki 21:1</a> <br/> - Naboth's vineyard in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=1'>1Ki 21:1</a> <br/> - Joram's residence in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=8&verse=29'>2Ki 8:29</a> <br/> - Jehu kills King Ahab, his wife, and friends at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=9&verse=37'>2Ki 9:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=11'>2Ki 10:11</a> <br/> - Prophecies concerning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=1&verse=5'>Hos 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=1&verse=11'>Hos 1:11</a> <br/> 3. A valley<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=17&verse=16'>Jos 17:16</a><br/> - Place of Gideon's battle with the Midianites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=33'>Jdg 6:33</a> <br/> - Place of the defeat of the Israelites under Saul and Jonathan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=29&verse=1'>1Sa 29:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=29&verse=11'>1Sa 29:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=31&verse=6'>1Sa 31:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=4&verse=4'>2Sa 4:4</a> <br/> 4. A descendant of Etam<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=4&verse=3'>1Ch 4:3</a><br/> 5. Figurative of Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=1&verse=5'>Hos 1:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=1&verse=11'>Hos 1:11</a>"}]}